1. U petak samo šetamo *noću* (We are only walking at night.)
2. *Noći* su dugačke, ali to nas ne sprječava da se zabavimo (The nights are long, but that doesn't stop us from having fun.)
3. Prekrasan *noćni* pogled na grad (A beautiful night view of the city.)
4. *Noći* su bile tople (The nights were warm.)
5. Imamo malo slobodnog vremena za razgledanje *noću* (We have a little free time to explore at night.)